'''恩宠之母圣殿'''（Basilica of Our Lady of Graces）是一座[[罗马天主教|罗马天主教]][[宗座圣殿|宗座圣殿]]，位于[[印度|印度]][[北方邦|北方邦]][[密拉特县|密拉特县]][[萨尔达纳|萨尔达纳]]，在[[密拉特|密拉特]]西北19公里处。<ref>{{Cite journal | url = https://books.google.com/?id=oXWAEjcG-FsC&pg=PA20&dq=sardhana+church#v=onepage&q=sardhana%20church&f=false | title = Tourism Marketing | isbn = 9788131731826 | author1 = Devashish | first1 = Dasgupta | year = 2011}}</ref> 

